00:40:13,482 --> 00:40:14,441
Not yet.

524
00:40:17,069 --> 00:40:18,570
Well...

525
00:40:18,654 --> 00:40:20,698
let me know when he does.

526
00:40:20,781 --> 00:40:24,201
Everything we've talked about
so far falls apart

