to make sure

558
00:42:30,577 --> 00:42:34,164
America lives up
at its end of the bargain.

559
00:42:34,248 --> 00:42:36,083
It will.

560
00:42:36,166 --> 00:42:40,629
Then, yes, we have a deal.

561
00:42:40,712 --> 00:42:41,797
And you'll declare an immediate
country-wide cease fire

562
00:42:41,880 --> 00:42:44,132
as we discussed?

563
00:42:46,301 --> 00:42:49,638
Starting tomorrow morning.

564
00:42:57,813 --> 00:43:01,316
What's wrong?

565
00:43:01,400 --> 00:43:04,903
I'm worried I made a mistake
with Jalal.

566
00:43:04,987 --> 00:43:05,737
By letting him go?

567
00:43:05,821 --> 00:43:08,991
Hmm.

568
00:43:09,074 --> 00:43:11,410
By not putting
his head in a bag

569
