00:46:43,622 --> 00:46:46,249
I have, sir.

648
00:46:46,333 --> 00:46:49,377
<i>Well, I appreciate
the bluntness.</i>

649
00:46:49,461 --> 00:46:51,630
<i>Now, if you don't mind,
