650
00:46:51,713 --> 00:46:53,924
<i>with my
National Security Advisor.</i>

651
00:46:54,007 --> 00:46:55,467
Yes, sir.

652
00:46:55,550 --> 00:46:57,385
<i>Saul, Carrie...</i>

653
00:46:57,469 --> 00:46:58,804
<i>Thank you, David.</i>

654
00:47:00,305 --> 00:47:03,642
<i>Talk to me, Saul.</i>

655
00:47:03,725 --> 00:47:05,727
Well, sir, the best part
